WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.000
Well these charges are opposite. One is a positive and one is a negative.

00:00:03.000 --> 00:00:06.000
Opposite charges attract so they'll come together.

00:00:06.000 --> 00:00:10.000
This is actually deeply fascinating and has some serious implications

00:00:10.000 --> 00:00:15.000
for well everything from the structure of matter to--well-- lightning

00:00:15.000 --> 00:00:21.000
because a lone positive charge and a lone negative charge when left their own devices pair up.

00:00:21.000 --> 99:59:59.000
Let's take a look at the consequences of this pairing up.

